{"tid":2264315,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國拒「封城」　執政保守黨民望被工黨超越","createTime":"2020-10-30T14:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T15:39:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e351b5b29916d9817ed5f348070f11b50377abf6","tid":2264315,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557579-20201030.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557579-20201030.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdt7g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=e65b914f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557579-20201030.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e7b0fc31\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557579-20201030.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國政府拒絕實施全國封鎖，應對肺炎疫情。<br />\n<br />\n英國過去一星期平均每日錄得逾二萬宗確診病例，但政府拒絕效法德國和法國，重新「封城」。<br />\n<br />\n外相藍鞱文為此辯護說，封城不是無可避免，雖然情況嚴峻，但對政府的做法有信心。他說，自從採用分級制應付疫情以來，已經有證據顯示病例增長下降，但補充說大家必須遵守法規。<br />\n<br />\n藍鞱文表示，當局避免採取更嚴厲措施，以免對經濟產生影響。<br />\n<br />\n另外，民調顯示，執政保守黨的支持度下滑至37%，被在野工黨的42%超越。首相約翰遜的支持淨值更跌至新低，反映民眾不滿政府疫情手法。"},{"pid":"0c79d5cdd5c520f7b616cda5332fedde09a317ef","tid":2264315,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"唔明點解左翼(或者叫做左膠)注重防疫多過右翼？"},{"pid":"57afd583acb9f4cc99374cb290eae91d2983e50e","tid":2264315,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"佢地好似無封關？<br />\n一日唔封 lockdown 幾多次都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}